'''掼奶油'''（{{lang-en|Whipped cream}}）或'''淡奶油'''，是经过打发的[[鲜奶油|鲜奶油]]。[[乳脂|乳脂]]含量不低于30%的液态奶油（whipping cream）在搅拌过程中与空气混和，逐渐变成蓬鬆的半液態[[胶体|軟膠]]狀，體積变为兩倍左右。

==历史==
生奶油在16世纪开始流行<ref name='scully'>Terence Scully, trans., ''The Opera of Bartolomeo Scappi (1570): L'arte et prudenza d'un maestro Cuoco; The Art and Craft of a Master Cook'', 2008, ISBN 0-8020-9624-7, [https://books.google.com/books?id=GrvhZvK5pCgC&pg=PA105 p. 105, note 2.39] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GrvhZvK5pCgC&pg=PA105 |date=20200530155429 }}, with many menus including "neve di latte servita con zuccaro sopra" 'milk snow with sugar on top', [https://books.google.com/books?id=GrvhZvK5pCgC&q=%22neve+di+latte%22 ''passim''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GrvhZvK5pCgC&q=%22neve+di+latte%22 |date=20200529051952 }}</ref>，在多本著作中有提及<ref>Catherine Frances Frere, ''Prepere newe Booke of Cokerye'', 1545 (modern edition 1913) -- cited in Scully</ref><ref>Michelle Berriedale-Johnson, ''Festive Feasts Cookbook'' (British Museum), 2004, ISBN 0-299-19510-4, [https://books.google.com/books?id=qiDBvjhUqnUC&pg=PA33 p. 33] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qiDBvjhUqnUC&pg=PA33 |date=20200530055755 }}, citing Messisbugo's ''Banchetti, composizioni di vivande e apparecchio generale''</ref><ref>''Ouverture de cuisine'',  "Pour faire neige", p. 123 [http://www.uni-giessen.de/gloning/tx/ouv3.htm transcription] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uni-giessen.de/gloning/tx/ouv3.htm |date=20120803085641 }}</ref>，曾被称为“牛奶雪”（英语：milk snow）<ref>Rabelais, ''Quart livre'', LIX, 1552, éd. R. Marichal, p. 241, cited in the ''Trésor de la langue française''</ref>。雪奶油（英语：snow cream）的名称一直到17世纪还在使用 <ref>''Dictionarium Rusticum, Urbanicum & Botanicum'', 1726, ''s.v.'' 'Syllabub' [https://books.google.com/books?id=v2FJAAAAYAAJ&pg=RA1-PT296 full text] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=v2FJAAAAYAAJ&pg=RA1-PT296 |date=20200531025322 }}</ref><ref>Sarah Harrison, ''The house-keeper's pocket-book, and compleat family cook'', 1749, p. 173. [https://books.google.com/books?id=3IcEAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA173 full text] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=3IcEAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA173 |date=20200529151652 }}</ref>。
==成分==
用于打发的奶油脂肪含量很高，因为脂肪颗粒容易形成包围气泡的稳定结构<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.uoguelph.ca/foodscience/book-page/whipped-cream-structure|title=Whipped Cream Structure {{!}} Food Science|website=www.uoguelph.ca|access-date=2020-01-04|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111015150/https://www.uoguelph.ca/foodscience/book-page/whipped-cream-structure|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一般打发奶油的乳脂含量在30%-36%之间， [[蛋白质|蛋白质]]含量在2.5-2.2%之间<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Aggarwal|first=M. L.|date=June 19, 1974|title=Ultra-Pasteurization of Whipping Cream|url=https://jfoodprotection.org/doi/pdf/10.4315/0022-2747-38.1.36|journal=Journal of Food and Milk Technology|volume=38|pages=36-38|via=}}</ref>。

打发奶油里会添加[[糖|糖]]，使其味道變甜。有時會搭配[[香莢蘭|香莢蘭]]或加入[[橙花水|橙花水]]調味。<ref>Jules Gouffée ''et al.'', ''Le livre de pâtisserie'', 1873 p. [https://archive.org/details/lelivredepatisse00gouf/page/138 138]</ref>
==制备==
===搅拌法===
传统方法是通過攪拌鮮奶油，直到它明亮和蓬鬆；將液態的鮮奶油不停地攪拌直到被打成蓬鬆的半液態軟膠狀，這是因為奶油中含有超過30%的[[脂肪|脂肪]]在攪拌過程中與空氣混和，空氣被油脂的網絡鎖住而導致得出來的奶油是攪拌前的大約兩倍體積<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Viet|last2=Cua|title=Effect of thermal treatment on physical properties and stability of whipping and whipped cream|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0260877415001934|journal=Journal of Food Engineering|volume= 163, October 2015, Pages 32–36}}</ref>。

打發之前最好是冷藏<ref>{{cite web|author1=Hirsheimer Hamilton|title=Whip it Real Good: How to Make Whipped Cream at Home|url=http://www.bonappetit.com/test-kitchen/common-mistakes/article/whipped-cream-common-mistakes|website=bon appetit|accessdate=2016-11-01|date=2014-11-19|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308143338/https://www.bonappetit.com/test-kitchen/common-mistakes/article/whipped-cream-common-mistakes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。如果在形成生奶油的狀態後繼續攪拌，油脂會黏在一起變成固體的[[黃油|奶油]]，其液態成分會被完全地分離出來成為[[白脫牛奶|白脫牛奶]]，這種奶因為上述原因所以其脂肪含量比一般的[[牛奶|牛奶]]要低<ref name='mcgee'>Harold McGee, ''On Food and Cooking'', p. 32</ref>。有時候為了令生奶油的質感更挺身及避免過度攪拌成牛油會在事前加入[[糖霜_(餐飲)|糖霜]]<ref>{{cite book|author1=E. Dentu|title=La Cuisine classique: études pratiques, raisonnées et démonstratives de l'Ecole française appliquée au service à la russe|date=1868|url=https://books.google.de/books?id=A7DX5_x_hrAC&pg=PA122&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2019-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014231906/https://books.google.de/books?id=A7DX5_x_hrAC&pg=PA122&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
===充气法===
[[File:SparkwhipNitrousChargerBack.JPG|thumb]]。]]
生奶油可以买现成的{{le|Reddi-Wip|Reddi-Wip|喷灌}}<ref>Wayne Gisslen, ''Professional Baking'', 2008, ISBN 0471783498, p. 264</ref>。但喷罐装挤出来已经打发好的奶油稳定性差，一般只用来装饰热饮和水果，不适合装饰蛋糕。自己制作时，将需要打发的奶油装入一个形状类似“保温杯”的喷枪（whipping siphon），装上一颗银色子弹大小的“{{le|奶油充气罐|Whipped-cream charger|气罐}}”，按动阀门，即可喷出打发的奶油。<ref name="lange">Aeration Processes, Inc. ''v.'' Lange ''et al.'', 196 F.2d 981, 93 USPQ 332, United States Court of Appeals Eighth Circuit, May 20, 1952.</ref>
==用途==
生奶油通常加在[[咖啡|咖啡]]或[[可可|可可]]飲料上<ref>{{cite book|author1=Jules Gouffé|title=Le livre de patisserie|date=1873|publisher=Hachette|url=https://books.google.de/books?id=eNUqAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA138&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false|accessdate=2016-11-01|archive-date=2019-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929084017/https://books.google.de/books?id=eNUqAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA138&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>，或塗在西式甜點上如[[蛋糕|蛋糕]]、[[派|派]]或[[雪糕|雪糕]]等<ref>Rose Levy Beranbaum, ''The Pie and Pastry Bible'', 2009, ISBN 1439130876, p. 550</ref>。可以使用[[擠花袋|擠花袋]]在糕點上擠出生奶油裝飾花紋，添加稳定剂可长时间保持形状<ref>Alan Imeson, ed., ''Food Stabilisers, Thickeners and Gelling Agents'', 2011, ISBN 1444360337, ''passim''</ref><ref>oetker.[http://www.oetker.ca/ca-en/our-products/dr-oetker-whip-it/dr-oetker-whip-it.html Dr. Oetker Whip It] {{Wayback|url=http://www.oetker.ca/ca-en/our-products/dr-oetker-whip-it/dr-oetker-whip-it.html |date=20190108044227 }}</ref>。
